ngel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜嘢想溝呀？我由頭到尾冇講過。係你自己講，即係呢個係你嘅諗法，不打自招。 不過以我嘅經驗，問得我嘅男仔全部都係溝我，除非係女仔問女仔。<br />\n<br />\n我就係話呢個係私隱嚟，同問人食咗飯未係完全唔同，係唔應該問。"},{"pid":"60b5ba5f0218939e5626b50e81f65659a91d8da9","tid":657704,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c1f5bd13b7771ba92fb06bf80ca060d6a6fe2f70","tid":657704,"uid":45831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"直接同佢講 有呀! 好似好唔理佢感受 一野收佢皮咁 攪到大家好尷尬<br />\n<br />\n如何婉轉d咁答等佢知已經有另一半 同時又俾到個落台楷佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"Sp？"},{"pid":"22a1364a9e479309187a595ee942d2494428d299","tid":657704,"uid":91767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T12:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>直接同佢講 有呀! 好似好唔理佢感受 一野收佢皮咁 攪到大家好尷尬<br />\n<br />\n如何婉轉d咁答等佢知已經有另一半 同時又俾到個落台楷佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>Sp？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsl比較好d"},{"pid":"fd6ed9eb4994807653f215ff448680216fb46ada","tid":657704,"uid":45831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2c1ff38f8f3259c6592d46d5bcecd0c89ad51f9","tid":657704,"uid":46410,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"「就算我無都唔會考慮你」🤷🏻&zwj;♀️"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T12:21:15.000Z","msg":"笑死 大巴大巴咁車埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72685448a8c3dc2b319df9d3086ac9ff516b7124","tid":657704,"uid":45831,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a2f09c12452062738e475b367c7f17a72f9666b","tid":657704,"uid":38904,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"拍拖只係暫時<br />\n機會卻唔會停止"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T12:21:46.000Z","msg":"收兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e6f7dce8451331327fd3dcc4e89fb031117af7","tid":657704,"uid":96007,"like":0,"dis